data.description: 1 Year Home Warranty for Buyer! Welcome to this well maintained 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home nestled in the highly sought-after Northwood neighborhood, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Located in close proximity to Morgan State University, this charming residence boasts a spacious living area highlighted by a large bay window, allowing natural light to flood the space and creating a warm, inviting atmosphere. With its well-maintained interiors and desirable location, this home presents an exceptional opportunity for comfortable living in a vibrant community. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your dream home! Brand NEW Furnace installed!
